
use this command when you are getting problem in updating android studio saying use as privileged user to opt/android-studio***
type following in terminal
sudo chown -R $USER:$USER /opt/android-studio
then from help->check updates
then download the update and install


or refer to for details****
http://bjubuntu.blogspot.com/2017/11/studio-does-not-have-write-access-to.html
